The Plot:
You are a Sergeant of the "Special-Forces" in the Mountains.


Your Missions:
Kill members of Al-Kaida and soldiers of Saddam Hussain's army!
(Earn so much points, it's possible!!!)


The control:
Just shoot (clicking) on the objects there came
on the black squares, if you miss, you lost 100 points!!!
You have max. 90 seconds (1:30 mins ) to kill so much
badguys you can, be quickly and fast !!!

 Hit fellowing keys
	on title:    Q = quitting game (press Y for Yes or N for no)
	during play: Q = leave/abort game
					 P = game paused


Fellowing objects exists in game:
	o a member of Al-Kaida¹

	o a soldiers of Saddam Hussain's army
		
	o A friendly soldier (looks like Saddam's soldier, but he has
	  a star on his hat and a beard)
	  If you hit him the game is over, immediately!!!

	o A Lady (Don't shoot her, or you loose all your points)

	o A Surprise can be:
		 10 secs and 250 points more
		 10 secs and 250 points less
		 500 points will increased your score
		 500 points will decreased your score


